On 6/20/03 6:42 AM, "John Baker" <harmony(-at-)buszen.com> wrote:

> On a late bay, which way should the engine compartment
> seal be installed, Shiny side up (in engine
> compartment) or shiny side down (under bus)?

There is some debate on the matter but on all the busses I've seen and based
on the pictures in the Bentley it goes shiny side down. Based on the parts
diagram it joins by the fan, not the firewall (#34):

